      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61524043.pdf_156_2",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "沿途经过村镇时，不时见",
        "bbox": [
          0.17636684066036648,
          0.7068251551021731,
          0.45414461470044365,
          0.7278348200096687
        ],
        "order": 4
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61524043.pdf_156_4",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "到路边有摆卖释迦的农舍。我在心中琢磨着，到这里了还不品尝一下， 似乎太对不起自己。",
        "bbox": [
          0.13447971600352943,
          0.7338375814118103,
          0.857583762711032,
          0.7818596726289432
        ],
        "order": 5
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61524043.pdf_156_5",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "看中一个大户人家，大大的凉棚，路边摆放着一筐筐的释迦，平板 上也摆满了，个个硕大饱满，颇为招惹人啊！",
        "bbox": [
          0.136684301511784,
          0.7878624340310847,
          0.857583762711032,
          0.8358845252482175
        ],
        "order": 6
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61524043.pdf_156_6",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "一打听，价格果然不菲，新台币要100元一斤。",
        "bbox": [
          0.18077601167687563,
          0.8418872866503592,
          0.6481481394268468,
          0.8628969515578547
        ],
        "order": 7
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61524043.pdf_156_7",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "我让老板娘特意挑选了一粒成熟的释迦给我，75元成交。",
        "bbox": [
          0.17857142616862107,
          0.8704004033105317,
          0.7517636583148121,
          0.8884086875169565
        ],
        "order": 8
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61524043.pdf_156_8",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "“这个怎么吃啊？！”我也不怕老板娘笑话我，没吃过就是没吃过，",
        "bbox": [
          0.16754849862734814,
          0.8959121392696335,
          0.8553791772027773,
          0.9169218041771291
        ],
        "order": 9
      }
